# This main program is used for the test of flame graph. The program flamegraph.pl and stackcollapse-perf.pl come
# from the repo https://github.com/brendangregg/FlameGraph.git

1. How to generate flame graph
A. make flame-graph
   http://10.124.114.236/linux-perf/flame-graph/main.fg.svg

2. How to get the perf report
A. make report

# Below perf report shows that the calcute function has almost 100% overhead which means this function
# is the one which impact the performance. It also shows the callchain of the program main where how the
# is called in the main whole call stack.
